ver cod and set aside."},{"content":"Place water in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket then weigh in potatoes. Sprinkle with salt then steam <b>12 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Place Varoma dish into position and weigh in broccoli. Cover Varoma then steam <b>10-15 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b> until cooked. Meanwhile, place tray with cod in oven and bake for 12-15 minutes (180°C) until cooked (will depend on thickness of fish)."},{"content":"Slice cod into 6 portions (if not already) then divide steamed broccoli between 6 plates and place cod on top. Serve with steamed potatoes and cherry tomatoes on the side, finishing with a drizzle of oil."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This dish is a complete meal to feed all the family – two vegetable sides complement the flavoursome topped fish. To make <i>Cornbread<\/i> for the topping, refer to Cookidoo.","Try black olives or a mixture of both."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","40m","6 portions"]}